ol&amp;author=M+Prokop&amp;author=RP+Budde&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Eur+Radiol&amp;pages=1271-1277&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00330-011-2358-1&amp;pmid=22205446">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">19.</div><div id="r19" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Habets J, van den Brink RB, Uijlings R, et al. Coronary artery assessment by multidetector computed tomography in patients with prosthetic heart valves. <em>Eur Radiol</em> 2012;22(6):1278–1286.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00330-011-2360-7">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22193371/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Coronary+artery+assessment+by+multidetector+computed+tomography+in+patients+with+prosthetic+heart+valves&amp;author=J+Habets&amp;author=RB+van+den+Brink&amp;author=R+Uijlings&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Eur+Radiol&amp;pages=1278-1286&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00330-011-2360-7&amp;pmid=22193371">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">20.</div><div id="r20" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">LaBounty TM, Agarwal PP, Chughtai A, Bach DS, Wizauer E, Kazerooni EA. Evaluation of mechanical heart valve size and function with ECG-gated 64-MDCT. <em>AJR Am J Roentgenol</em> 2009;193(5):W389–W396.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.2214/AJR.08.2178">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19843716/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Evaluation+of+mechanical+heart+valve+size+and+function+with+ECG-gated+64-MDCT&amp;aut